title: Meet a Pro with the Society of Women Engineers on Oct. 15 (University of Arkansas) ...
text: ( Source : University of Arkansas ) Courtesy of the Society of Women Engineers Society of Women Engineers hosts ' Meet a Pro.' All students are invited to come to the 'Meet a Pro' event hosted by Society of Women Engineers from 5-7 p.m.
